            <p>While FXIFY offers a 5-day "Lightning Challenge", their flagship <strong>Two Phase Pro Account</strong> completely removes the time limit while giving you the best risk parameters in the industry.</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-slate-300 mb-6">
            <li><strong>Unlimited Days + Static Drawdown:</strong> Take as long as you need to hit the Phase 1 target, and rest easy knowing your 8% maximum drawdown is completely static (it never trails up).</li>
            <li><strong>On-Demand Payouts:</strong> Once funded, you don't have to wait 30 days to get paid. You can request a withdrawal immediately after your first winning trade.</li>
            <li><strong>Broker Backed:</strong> Directly partnered with FXPIG for genuine <a href="/blog/zero-spread-brokers-stop-loss-hunting/" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">ECN/STP execution</a>.</li>
            </ul>
            <p><a href="/prop-firms/fxify/" class="inline-block mt-2 text-sm font-bold bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg transition-colors">Read FXIFY Review & Get 33% OFF →</a></p>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-400 mt-12 mb-4">2. Darwinex Zero (The Best Institutional & No Fails)</h3>
            <p>If FTMO’s strict "breach rules" stress you out, <strong>Darwinex Zero</strong> offers a completely different, highly regulated path with absolutely zero time pressure.</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-slate-300 mb-6">
            <li><strong>No Fails or "Breaches":</strong> They evaluate your Value at Risk (VaR). If your strategy hits a slump, you don’t lose your account. There are no time limits to prove your consistency.</li>
            <li><strong>MT4/MT5 for US Traders:</strong> Because it is an FCA-regulated broker operating a virtual seed capital model, Darwinex Zero legally allows <a href="/blog/prop-firms-accepting-us-traders/" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">US residents</a> to trade on MetaTrader terminals.</li>
            <li><strong>Institutional Scaling:</strong> Access a pool of over <strong>€100+ million</strong> in real third-party investor capital once you prove your edge.</li>
            </ul>
            <p><a href="/prop-firms/darwinex-zero/" class="inline-block mt-2 text-sm font-bold bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg transition-colors">Read Darwinex Zero Review & Get 20% OFF →</a></p>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-400 mt-12 mb-4">3. DNA Funded (Best for Multi-Asset Diversification)</h3>
            <p>Backed by the ASIC-regulated DNA Markets, <strong>DNA Funded</strong> is an absolute powerhouse for portfolio traders who want to trade 800+ assets without deadlines.</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-slate-300 mb-6">
            <li><strong>Zero Deadlines:</strong> Both their 1-Phase and 2-Phase evaluations feature completely unlimited trading days.</li>
            <li><strong>Weekend Holding:</strong> Because there is no ticking clock, you are allowed to hold trades over the weekend on crypto assets and FX.</li>
            <li><strong>800+ Tradable Assets:</strong> Massive lists of individual equities, deep crypto markets, and FX via MT5 or TradeLocker.</li>
            </ul>
            <p><a href="/prop-firms/dna-funded/" class="inline-block mt-2 text-sm font-bold bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg transition-colors">Read DNA Funded Review & Get 25% OFF →</a></p>

