            <td class="px-6 py-4 border-l border-slate-800 text-emerald-400 font-bold">Unlimited</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 border-l border-slate-800">None</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 border-l border-slate-800">VaR Based (No Breach)</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 border-l border-slate-700">Hedge Fund Scaling</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="hover:bg-slate-800/30 transition-colors">
            <td class="px-6 py-4 font-bold text-blue-400">DNA Funded</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 border-l border-slate-800 text-emerald-400 font-bold">Unlimited</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 border-l border-slate-800">5 Days</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 border-l border-slate-800">Static (Depending on Phase)</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 border-l border-slate-800">800+ Assets</td>
            </tr>
            </tbody>
            </table>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">Conclusion: Protect Your Psychology</h2>
            <p>Trading is 90% psychology and 10% strategy. When you remove the arbitrary 30-day time limit, you stop revenge trading, you stop taking C-tier setups, and you allow your statistical edge to play out naturally in the market.</p>
            <p>If you are ready to trade the way institutions actually trade—without a ticking clock—grab an unlimited challenge from <a href="/prop-firms/fxify/" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">FXIFY</a> or <a href="/prop-firms/darwinex-zero/" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">Darwinex Zero</a> and use our <a href="/#compare" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">verified promo codes</a> to get funded cheaper today.</p>
          </div>

          <footer class="mt-20 pt-12 border-t border-slate-900">
