                <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top_right,_var(--tw-gradient-stops))] from-blue-600/5 via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 relative z-10">Don't Forget Your Free MT5 Tools</h3>
